replies.body:
That's pretty awesome bro, congrats on graduating!!!
{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 

Honestly, I don't have much info on where you should go or who to speak to, but you might be able to get a start by hitting us up via e-mail at info@riotgames.com. We do some work with our Summoner's here and there, and who knows, maybe you'd be a great addition to the team sometime!
